# Minimal CarpetX + WeakLibInterp thorn list (specs/cactus-integration.md §79,
# verification item 5): the CarpetX driver's required capability set
# (AMReX IOUtil MPI yaml_cpp zlib + Arith/CarpetXRegrid/Loop), the
# WeakLibInterp wrapper thorn, and the scratch consumer thorn that calls one
# _Point per kernel family. ADIOS2 / openPMD / Silo / NSIMD are OPTIONAL for
# CarpetX and deliberately omitted.

CactusBase/IOUtil

ExternalLibraries/AMReX
ExternalLibraries/HDF5
ExternalLibraries/MPI
ExternalLibraries/yaml_cpp
ExternalLibraries/zlib

CarpetX/Arith
CarpetX/CarpetX
CarpetX/CarpetXRegrid
CarpetX/Loop

WeakLibInterp/WeakLibInterp
WeakLibInterp/WeakLibInterpTest
